2026-02-10CIRCBritish Columbia Treaty Commission ActRe-appointment of the Commissioner of the British Columbia Treaty CommissionRe-appointment of Liseanne Forand of North Saanich, British Columbia, as a Commissioner of the British Columbia Treaty Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, or until such time as a new Commissioner is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective July 1, 2026.N/A
subject: Re-appointment of the Commissioner of the British Columbia Treaty Commission
precis: Re-appointment of Liseanne Forand of North Saanich, British Columbia, as a Commissioner of the British Columbia Treaty Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, or until such time as a new Commissioner is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective July 1, 2026.
